<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Consensus on Aman Goyal</title><link>https://goyal-aman.github.io/blog/consensus/</link><description>Recent content in Consensus on Aman Goyal</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-US</language><copyright>Copyright © 2025, Aman Goyal.</copyright><lastBuildDate>Sat, 14 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://goyal-aman.github.io/blog/consensus/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Leader Election: Ensuring a Single Owner in a Distributed System</title><link>https://goyal-aman.github.io/leader-election-ensuring-a-single-owner-in-a-distributed-system/</link><pubDate>Sat, 14 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://goyal-aman.github.io/leader-election-ensuring-a-single-owner-in-a-distributed-system/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="core-concept"&gt;Core Concept&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ownership / Leader election = only one replica owns a task at a time&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Needed for:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scheduling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shard ownership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background jobs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implemented via:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Distributed locks over KV stores (etcd, ZooKeeper, Consul)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id="do-you-even-need-leader-election"&gt;Do You Even Need Leader Election?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Singleton approach&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Simple&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Downtime during failures or deploys&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use leader election only when:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You need &lt;strong&gt;high availability (4+ nines)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id="core-primitive-compare-and-swap"&gt;Core Primitive: Compare-And-Swap&lt;/h2&gt;
